description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, Tim Cowlishaw of the Dallas Morning News calls in to discuss the hot start to the season for Cowboys. Are there any question marks on this team? ESPN's Mina Kimes ranks the AFC and NFC teams. And Carson Palmer makes his weekly pitt stop and talks about getting called out by a coach.
